snippet.title: Slendrina X Trailer
snippet.description:
This is Slendrina X! The 10th slendrina game in this series!
This time you are a prisoner in a big castle that belongs to Slendrinas husband.
You have to escape to complete the game by finding the entrance key.
Slendrina is watching you as always and her husband is walking around the dark corridors, and he is mad.
Watch out for him and his 2 pets that bites hard.

The game is free but it Contains advertising.

Good luck!

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dvloper.slendrinax


"To all iOS players, I only want to announce that Slendrina X will not be published on App Store because the company Apple has not approved this game. I have done my best to publish it on the App Store but unfortunately it did not work. (The same applies to The Child of Slendrina). I am so sorry for this.
Best regards,
DVloper"
